@node status "Status"

@{fg shine}STATUS@{fg text}

Circuit is public domain.
the AmigaE source is included, so you can help me to enhance my program, look in it to know how I did a thing or find a bug in it.
You can ask me if there is something you don't understand in this source.
Note that I don't know if everything in that source is legal and that there are no better way to do it.
There are also maybe things that are completely wrong, that should never be done. (Even if I hope not :-)

@{fg shine}WARRANTY@{fg text}

What warranty? If Circuit does crash your system, erase your hard drive or give you wrong results, if you lose all your money because you used a circuit of my program that was badly interpreted or anything else, NO WARRANTY are given. (But say me if you had such trouble with my program, I may try to fix the problem)

